{
  "stem": "20580.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I haven't got in city where to keep it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I give to a guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He kept a week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then my brother went and get milk every week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, I had-- always, a cow, two cows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I bought them myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was $50, so a lot of money that time. $40 a cow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now, in one time, I lost $5.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother told me-- I'll never forget-- you're a businessman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If you're losing-- making money, you're not a businessman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But if you could lose $5, $6, then you're in the business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You'll get next week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I remember every story my mother used to tell me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Sadder stories.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Which I'd remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She was very smart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I used to come in-- they call it the [NON-ENGLISH], advisors, [NON-ENGLISH] in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They-- and a lady come, she have a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Doesn't cost her any money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I know Midel is smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And she says, I have two boys for my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "One is this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "One is-- they call it [NON-ENGLISH], a primitive man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It's the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Basically it's [NON-ENGLISH], a-- a-- a truck driver, you know, in a-- all driver.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "This guy, basically, she says, if you get married, you have to expect to get a divorce.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "The negative in marriage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You have to get divorced.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Tell them, you get divorced, he says, son of a bitch, I don't need you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "You don't know-- the other guy says, listen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "The rabbi calls him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He assess them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "You have to divorce nicely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "She's a human being.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], he says.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You have to divorce.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then you have to-- to-- to go to rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And tell him you haven't got anywhere to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "He's going to do it by himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I've been with her to the movies with my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
